<h3>Feats</h3>
In this step you will choose only one feat. Unless otherwise stated in classes or races.
At first level you get one feat for level. If you are a Human you get an extra feat. If you are a fighter you get an extra feat. As you level up you get more feats.
You get another feat at 3rd level, 6th level, 9th level, 12th level, 15th level, and 18th level.
